  "contentHtml": "<div><div><div><div><div><div><p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">根据《福建省教育厅办公室关于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">年度本科专业申报工作的通知》（闽教办高〔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">〕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">号）精神，现对我校</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">年新申报的听力与言语康复学、康复物理治疗、康复作业治疗等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">个本科专业设置申请表（备案专业适用），进行公示。公示时间：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">13-19</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 22.5pt;\">日，公示期间，如有异议，请与教务处联系。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:40.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.5;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">监督举报电话<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>工作日时间<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 63pt; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">0591-22861008(</span><span style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 63pt; font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体;\">教务处<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">18960879700</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:40.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.5;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">邮箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"mailto:fjtcm10393@163.com\">fjtcm10393@163.com</a>(</span>教务处<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">1. </span>听力与言语康复学本科专业设置申请表<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.0;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">&nbsp; 2.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">康复物理治疗本科专业设置申请表<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.0;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">&nbsp; 3.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">康复作业治疗本科专业设置申请表<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.0;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:4.0;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:212.35pt;mso-char-indent-count:23.5;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 教务处<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:194.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:21.5;\r\nline-height:18.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2017</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:302.2pt;mso-char-indent-count:21.5\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:15.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b></p></p>\n\n                        \t\n\n\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>",
  "contentText": "根据《福建省教育厅办公室关于 2017 年度本科专业申报工作的通知》（闽教办高〔 2017 〕 8 号）精神，现对我校 2017 年新申报的听力与言语康复学、康复物理治疗、康复作业治疗等 3 个本科专业设置申请表（备案专业适用），进行公示。公示时间： 2017 年 7 月 13-19 日，公示期间，如有异议，请与教务处联系。 监督举报电话 ( 工作日时间 ) ： 0591-22861008( 教务处 ) ， 18960879700 邮箱： fjtcm10393@163.com ( 教务处 ) 附件 1. 听力与言语康复学本科专业设置申请表 2. 康复物理治疗本科专业设置申请表 3. 康复作业治疗本科专业设置申请表 教务处 2017 年 7 月 13 日",
